[Instructions to get plop-plop running]

1. Install dependencies
=======================

- Install virtualenv
- Install pip
- Install phonegap 2.7
- Install Android SDK
- Install transcompiler-watcher (https://github.com/nubela/transcompiler-watcher)
$ virtualenv v_env
$ source v_env/bin/activate #this will activate the jailed environment
$ pip install -r REQUIREMENTS
$ cp _cfg.py cfg.py #copy config template
$ vi cfg.py


2. How to use plop-plop
=======================

(To create a new project)

$ source v_env/bin/activate
$ python plop.py new <PROJECT_NAME>

(Create the bitbucket repositories)

$ python plop.py add_repo <PROJECT_NAME>